["addation_6dbd1344115ed969"] = "OK gang，we have received a communique from the Elephant。He claims to want to help us。Seems that in the early 1900s，a Kataru member stole what he calls \"a family heirloom\"。This person then bought his way onto the famous Shacklethorne expedition bound for Antarctica。His presence，according to the Elephant，doomed the voyage from the start。The familiarity of this is not a coincidence，despite the Elephant\"s caginess。The ship and crew were lost，until recently，when the wreckage was found crushed in the ice，far from the original planned route。A couple of miles from the wreckage，they also found a mummified corpse who looks to have died rather horrifically，and a sled along with a collection of artifacts。The items recovered are going to be auctioned in secret to a bunch of decadent society types，and the Elephant says that one of those items will help us with the device in the kitchen。I have a strange feeling about this one。It hits rather close to home。",  -- 语音文本，没有翻的必要(

